{"tid":1547629,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"只要美斯願意，每季結束後可與巴塞解約","createTime":"2019-09-06T17:22:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T02:45:42.000Z","uid":173952,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c73861bb54088ea66e6caa4d307aee1f546410cc","tid":1547629,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T17:22:03.000Z","msg":"根據西班牙媒體《國家報》報導稱，只要美斯（L.Messi）願意，他可以在每個賽季結束後單方面選擇與巴塞隆拿解除合約。<br />\n  報導稱，自從2005年以來，這名傳奇前鋒已經和球隊續約8次。在這份2017年夏天簽訂的合約當中保留著一份單方面條款，美斯可以在2021年合約結束之前隨時選擇在當賽季結束後終止合約。<br />\n  對此一名不願意透露姓名的巴塞隆拿球會內部人士表示：「在每個賽季結束時，美斯可以隨時選擇終止他和球隊的合約，這是我們同意的。」<br />\n  這種關係也是建立在巴塞隆拿球會對於美斯無條件信任的基礎上，他們相信在任何情況下，都不會有一支球隊會讓美斯做出離開巴塞隆拿的選擇。"},{"pid":"3ea9e284b09dbb3f645da216f4bd3e206e1453e8","tid":1547629,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T17:23:48.000Z","msg":"18輸比皇馬,買C朗<br />\n19輸比阿積士,買迪列治<br />\n如果20輸比巴塞會買邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdcb283df17e427b30c4561428e81eeb551a4022","tid":1547629,"uid":20809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T17:27:02.000Z","msg":"美斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e4ccbe625b41603fc290c49b8ea65f6bb570901","tid":1547629,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T17:30:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一句講晒，睇哩個post</span></span><br />\n[置頂/請廣傳/多圖] 907 遊客LOOK 暢遊大嶼山指南<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1547426\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1547426</a>"},{"pid":"9f21ed8d32b17e7145cd35018cbe8bc44a0c01dd","tid":1547629,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ea9e284b09dbb3f645da216f4bd3e206e1453e8","tid":1547629,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":4,"sco